68-// ======================================================================
69-//
70-// Plan 17-03 R3-03a + HIGH-3 (Option A):
71-//   The Direct3d11_PerMaterialCB shadow that backs the slot-b2 PerMaterial
72-//   cbuffer is PROMOTED to a file-scope static inside Direct3d11.cpp (no
73-//   longer the function-local static at the old :667 inside
74-//   setPixelShaderUserConstants_impl). Two code paths now read-modify-write
75-//   into the SAME shared shadow and both flush the FULL struct via updatePS
76-//   (most-recent write per field wins):
77-//
78-//     1. Direct3d11.cpp setPixelShaderUserConstants_impl()       (userConstants[])
79-//     2. Direct3d11_StaticShaderData::apply() per-pass material upload
80://        (materialDiffuse / materialSpecular / materialEmissive — when the
81-//        reflected cbuffer at the bound PS exposes those variables AND
82-//        layout.BindPoint == 2; per R3-03c the apply() upload is generally
83-//        offset-aware against the cached reflection layout regardless of
84-//        bind point, and the shadow mirror lives here ONLY for the slot-b2
85-//        case so setPixelShaderUserConstants_impl's slot-2 flush sees
86-//        consistent material values).
87-//
88-//   The getter is DECLARED here (the header that already owns
89-//   Direct3d11_PerMaterialCB) and DEFINED in Direct3d11.cpp (where the file-
90-//   scope shadow lives). Direct3d11_StaticShaderData.cpp includes this
91-//   header and calls Direct3d11Namespace::getPerMaterialShadow().
92-//
--
