181-//
182-// Direct3d11_VertexSlot0CB
183-//
184-// Plan 11-08 Task 2.5 + Task 3a: full slot-0 cbuffer for the VS, sized to
185:// match the shader's packoffset declarations in vertex_shader_constants.inc.
186-// Layout locked at planning time per CODEX Q3a ratification + the Iter-13B
187-// shader IR dump (stage/shader-iter13b-inc-0-output.txt). Per-field
188-// static_assert constellation below enforces every packoffset boundary at
189-// compile time so any future drift -- C++ side OR HLSL side -- surfaces as
190-// a build error, never a runtime NaN cascade / BSOD.
191-//
192-// Memory layout (all offsets in bytes, mapped to HLSL c-register slots):
193-//
194-//   c0..c3   offset    0   objectWorldCameraProjectionMatrix (WVP)    64B
195-//   c4..c7   offset   64   objectWorldMatrix (World)                  64B
196-//   c8..c10  offset  128   fog region                                 48B
197-//   c11..c15 offset  176   material                                   80B

